title: And Baby!
description:
It’s gonna be a huge weekend for Lala & Randall!  The big gender reveal of Baby Emmett is happening in Santa Barbara on Saturday, and Lala’s sharing all the juicy details! She and Rand are also voting on some names (and you’re invited to weigh in), and giving an update on everything baby. Plus, Lala’s spillin’ the tea on Denise Richards' exit from RHOBH and speculating on a new season of Vanderpump Rules!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
